    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 2D pixel art roguelike space shooter with plugged resource management, procedural levels and challenging bosses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold the controls tight and do not get stranded in the void! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234850/extras/f68a66fa2aca4c1fbad89c85a0e8e0b0.webp?t=1772467258\" width=454 height=28 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234850/extras/fd39236de4fd2305a07ae149dbc1ed2d.poster.avif?t=1772467258\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234850/extras/fd39236de4fd2305a07ae149dbc1ed2d.webm?t=1772467258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234850/extras/fd39236de4fd2305a07ae149dbc1ed2d.mp4?t=1772467258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plug in to recharge your energy and manage your resources.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be Careful! Once plugged, you'll only be able to move within the range of your cable!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space is plunged into darkness, activate the spacesockets to clear a level and travel to the next sector.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234850/extras/010a023bbb9a953d74b14f9b00a5d411.webp?t=1772467258\" width=232 height=28 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234850/extras/621d74591834d0221ec25510225abf7e.poster.avif?t=1772467258\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234850/extras/621d74591834d0221ec25510225abf7e.webm?t=1772467258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234850/extras/621d74591834d0221ec25510225abf7e.mp4?t=1772467258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose between <strong>10+ different ships </strong>with<strong> different gameplay modes!</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast your <strong>mega-laser!</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Form an <strong>army </strong>of rescued <strong>stranded ships</strong> that will fight alongside you!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Destroy </strong>the stages and defeat a large variety of enemies!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter dangerous and challenging <strong>BOSSES </strong>after each galaxy in your quest.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234850/extras/a7960c03bd088a760804db5121f1dee9.webp?t=1772467258\" width=478 height=28 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234850/extras/17a3dca76c9623829ba99350e52c8019.poster.avif?t=1772467258\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234850/extras/17a3dca76c9623829ba99350e52c8019.webm?t=1772467258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234850/extras/17a3dca76c9623829ba99350e52c8019.mp4?t=1772467258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Holding the breach, dodging enemy bullets, and piloting through narrow hallways shouldn't be a problem, BUT just in case... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your ship is equipped with a futuristic <strong>Slow-Mo System</strong> that you can use <strong>almost whenever you want!</strong> </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Luckily for you, it<strong> recharges by collecting energy from dead enemies!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234850/extras/b7a391ab83193921044da5d2c3190b0d.webp?t=1772467258\" width=298 height=28 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up <strong>BATTERIES </strong>and discover <strong>+250 combinations</strong> of bullet modifiers!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get <strong>CHIPS </strong>of temporary upgrades by destroying enemies!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose between <strong>more than 40 upgrades for your ship.</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optimize charge times, improve your firepower, get more cable length...</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become <strong>invisible </strong>to enemies.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more!</p></li></ul>",
